nexml.^ot:comment:
Two taxon labels do not match (given as tribes because the genera were not determined).

Note, the topology of this tree was recreated manually (by G. Zhang) from the pdf of the publication. It has not been checked for accuracy against the published figure by the curator. Outgroup taxa were added and grouped in the tree based on taxonomy because they were not rendered in any tree in the publication.
nexml.^ot:studyPublicationReference: McKenna, D. D., A. S. Sequeira, A. E. Marvaldi, B. D. Farrell. 2009. Temporal lags and overlap in the diversification of weevils and flowering plants. Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences 106 (17: 7083-7088
